en_814374_0	Brigadier Nishantha Herath took up duties as the new Director Training of the Sri Lanka Army this morning (20) at the Army Headquarters in Sri Jayewardenepura.
en_814374_1	Amid ‘Pirith’ chanting of the members of Maha Sangha, the new Director Training signified the acceptance of his office at the auspicious minute.
en_814374_2	Staff Officers of the Directorate and Other Ranks attended the occasion.
